@startuml
skinparam Style strictuml
skinparam SequenceMessageAlignment center

actor "Train (Client)" as Train
participant "WebSocket Handler" as WS
participant "ConnectionManager" as CM
participant "UdpReceiverService" as UDP
participant "VideoBroadcastService" as Broadcast
actor "Utilisateur (Navigateur)" as User

== 1. Initialisation & Enregistrement ==

Train -> WS: Connexion WS (/ws/T1?type=train)
WS -> CM: AddClient(T1, Session_ABC)
Train -> WS: JSON { "type": "register_ssrc", "ssrc": 12345 }
WS -> CM: RegisterSessionSsrc(Session_ABC, 12345)
note right of CM: Map SSRC 12345 -> Train T1

== 2. Abonnement Utilisateur ==

User -> Broadcast: GET /video/T1
Broadcast -> CM: Vérifier si T1 existe
User -> Broadcast: Ouverture flux (multipart/x-mixed-replace)

== 3. Flux Vidéo (Temps Réel) ==

loop Transmission des images
    Train -> UDP: Paquets RTP (UDP 5004) [SSRC: 12345]
    UDP -> UDP: Réassemblage de l'image (Marker Bit)
    UDP -> CM: GetTrainIdBySsrc(12345)
    CM --> UDP: Retourne "T1"
    UDP -> Broadcast: DispatchFrame("T1", byte[] data)
    Broadcast -> User: Envoi du segment JPEG (--frame)
end

== 4. Déconnexion ==

User -> Broadcast: Ferme la page
Broadcast -> CM: Unsubscribe / Nettoyage Channel

Train -> WS: Close WebSocket
WS -> CM: RemoveClient(Session_ABC)
CM -> CM: Révocation SSRC 12345
@endum